Description:
A Quality Favourite In A Looked For Location!
This quality-built home in the sought-after Clyde Springs Estate matches its easy livability with an easy to live with location.
Stone tops, stainless steel appliances, an abundance of storage and preparation space and a long breakfast bench, anchors the expansive open plan living-meals. Finished with easy care floor tiles, it enjoys a seamless transition to the generous alfresco in a low-maintenance rear yard.
Occupants of the main bedroom can make the most of a walk-in robe and deluxe stone ensuite fitted with an oversize shower. Those in the remaining bedrooms will be very happy with their stone detailed bathroom complete with a deep soaker tub.
Ducted heating and cooling, double garage with rear roller door, quality window finishes, easy to live with landscaped gardens lead the list of sought-after inclusions. Within easy reach of Clyde Shopping Centre, public transport, schools and parks, its a home the whole family will love.

Description:
A STANDOUT ON EVERY LEVEL!
For the astute buyer that demands perfection & quality this stunning home is a must to inspect. Conveniently situated within the popular Clydevale Estate overlooking parklands, this Henley built family home showcases clean crisp finishes throughout, with display home quality fittings. Beyond the eye-catching front door you will be instantly impressed with what this home has to offer, your eyes will immediately be drawn to the engineered floorboards throughout leading to the outdoor entertaining area. The master bedrooms offers an impeccable ensuite with floor to ceiling tiles, double vanity, spa bath and fully fitted out WIR. The 3 further bedrooms to the rear of the home, all share a lovely floor to ceiling tiled bathroom and separate powder room. The open plan design offers a stunning functional kitchen with 40mm water fall bench tops, 90mm freestanding gas stove and electric oven, self-closing cabinetry and walk in pantry all overlooking a sizable family room and separate dining area. Both the theatre room and the dining have triple slide timber doors leading out to the grand sized alfresco entertaining area with electric illusion heater, gas built in BBQ and stone bench tops, perfect for large family gatherings. Other features include, double garage with built in cabinetry, ducted heating and 9kw reverse cycle split system.

Description:
COASTAL VILLAGE CUTIE !!
(1P3401) Don't blame me if you fall in love with this gorgeous 3 bedroom casa and with its coastal village lifestyle. This could be your dream home set on a huge 1366m² block or a development opportunity subject to council approval.
This home offers 3 bedrooms, open plan kitchen, living areas, heaps of tranquilly, a warm wood fire, split system AC, huge garage/man shed with its own dunnie, all on a 1366m² block.
Located in one of the area's most sought coastal villages, Warneet. Being only a short walk to the local boat ramp, parks, walking tracks, general store, only a 5 min drive to Tooradin and 10 min drive to Cranbourne, making this property ideally located for young families and/or people looking to live in a great neighborhood. Close to the water and not needing to drive for hours to throw a line in.
Don't miss the chance to secure a slice of coastal lifestyle!
For all enquiries call John Lauretta directly on 0421088646

Description:
Do you like the finer things in life?
Nestled away in Cranbourne North's Finest Locales, this stunning 5-bedroom home has been designed and built to perfection and boast features only some can dream of.
As you walk in the front door you instantly get the feeling that no stone has been left unturned, there is an overwhelming feeling of quality and thought that has been put into the home. Downstairs features a guest master suite, with full ensuite and walk in robe. Theatre room is decked out with state-of-the-art tech, leading through to the showpiece of the home, the centre hub Kitchen meals and dining. Again, no shortcuts here, waterfall stone bench-tops, 900mm appliances and a walk-in pantry that you could host a party in! All this adjoins the meals area and family living with gas log fireplace for the winter nights.
Leading upstairs, there is a further 4 bedrooms, the master is fit for a king and queen, with a huge ensuite with double shower, and a walk-in robe that will blow your socks off. In addition, the 3 further bedrooms has their own ensuite as well as walk in robes. A family living area upstairs tops it off for the kids to play and study.
Be the envy of all your friends and family, with an outdoor area that is nothing short of 10/10. The completely decked alfresco area with mains gas and power ready for you to enjoy a bbq, with bench seats overlooking the absolutely beautiful solar heated pool. A backyard like this doesn't get any better and is perfect for friends and family to enjoy.
Creature comforts include gas ducted heating and refrigerated cooling throughout, high ceilings, double garage with internal access and all this wrapped up on a substantial 512m2 (approx.) block in the most prestigious part of Tullilian Estate just meters from the original homestead with park like grounds and soaring trees.
This is a truly special home, one not to be missed. Call now for your inspection!
Internal area
390m²

Description:
approx 5 Acres in the heart of Cranbourne South
Escape the hustle and bustle of everyday life and experience country living on the cusp of suburbia, with this superb family residence on a verdant 5acres (approx.) providing a spectacular backdrop for the ultimate family lifestyle.
- Master bedroom boasting walk-in-robe and contemporary ensuite
- 3 additional bedrooms with built-in-robes, sharing a renovated family bathroom with freestanding bath and toilet, plus a full-sized laundry
- Generous entry foyer leading to the light-filled lounge and dining domain
- Central kitchen equipped with stone benches, glass splashbacks, Westinghouse stainless steel appliances, LG dishwasher, walk-in pantry plus an island breakfast bench
- Family room conveniently serviced by a servery window to the kitchen
- An alluring alfresco entertaining zone overlooks the sparkling, solar heated in-ground pool where summertime fun is certain to wow family and friends
- Ducted heating, split system air conditioning, alarm, bottled gas, septic tank, mains water
- Several paddocks providing the ideal space for livestock, supplemented by stables plus a large workshop/garage for equipment storage, plus a triple carport
Peaceful positioned in a location that provides convenient access to a plethora of sort-after amenities including close to Botanic Ridge Primary, Cranbourne South Primary, Cranbourne Secondary, Casey Grammar, transport, Cranbourne Botanic Gardens, playgrounds and reserves, plus Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre.
Photo ID is required at the open homes

Description:
CALL, EMAIL OR TEXT AGENT TO ARRANGE INSPECTION!
WHEN SIZE MATTERS!
Minutes from every conceivable amenity while enjoying the relaxed lifestyle that can only be found in the community of Junction Village, 27 Craig Road offers the best of both worlds with exceptional accommodation for the larger family or anyone who just wants space! No matter what ages, there's well zoned living and entertaining areas both inside and out providing space & privacy for everyone when it's needed.
THE HOME:
Downstairs - 4 bedrooms (one with it's own powder room) plus study, family bathroom complete with spa, lounge with wood fire and renovated fully appointed kitchen with ample bench & cupboard space that adjoins the meals & large living area
Upstairs - The perfectly zoned haven for grown ups! Comprising a relaxing retreat area adjoining the generous master bedroom with views over the Village Reserve! The master bedroom is further complemented with built in robes & of course the ensuite. Add to this the games room, this is a place you'll WANT to hang out!
OUTSIDE:
This property just keeps surprising! If there's not enough on offer inside, you're spoiled for choices outside. With room to park multiple cars securely to the front - or even boats/caravans/trailers, there's multiple choices for entertaining & even work from home options too!
The large covered entertaining area is designed to host the largest of family gatherings while the workshop with fitted benches and wood fire is the perfect man cave/work from home solution or extension of your entertaining area - whatever you need! Add to this the direct access available to you as the new owner to the Village Reserve, there's room to kick the footy, ride bikes, or have a hit of cricket just by walking through your back gate!
NEVER judge a book by it's cover This home MUST be inspected to be fully appreciated!
Noteable features:
Evaporative cooling
Split system
Freshly painted

NEAR NEW HOME IN PRIME LOCATION

This gorgeous, light filled and neat three-bedroom home has all the modern conveniences you desire. The generous master suite is positioned at the rear of home comprising a large walk-in robe and ensuite. The remaining 2 bedrooms are generously proportioned, complemented by built in robes and the stylish family bathroom.
This fabulous family home offers so many extras:
- Two living areas

- Gas ducted heating
- Evaporate cooling
- 900mm gas cooktop
- 600mm oven
- Feature tile splashback
- Dishwasher
- Blinds throughout

Located in the sought-after area of Clyde North in the Delaray Estate, this property takes full advantage of its surroundings and boasts numerous benefits. Experience the lifestyle you've always dreamed of!

38 SQUARES OF INSPIRED FAMILY LIVING
Offering a superb family floorpan, this stylish and beautifully upgraded Metricon home is a MUST inspect. The double storey delight sits proudly on 480m2 of land and offers light filled family living comprising:
Upstairs - 4 fantastic sized bedrooms, the master suite is super-sized with the most incredible walk through fitted robe and dual vanity ensuite with an oversized shower complete with dual shower heads and separate toilet. The remaining bedrooms all have walk in robes and are sized to easily accommodate queen size beds and are centrally located to the family bathroom (separate toilet) and the large activity area at the top of the stairs.
Downstairs: Upon entry prepare to be impressed with raised ceilings, and you will be drawn down the hallway past the large study/home office area and theatre room to the spacious light filled living area. The fully appointed kitchen is sure to impress the chef of the family with an incredible amount of stone bench top, masses of overhead cupboards, 900mm cooking, stainless steel dishwasher, upgraded tap ware and brilliantly fitted walk through pantry with the added convenience of direct access to the double remote garage.
Outside the home continues to impress with the alfresco area providing quality screens (1 which is remote operated) providing privacy and shelter, while the deck has been extended to cater for the larger gatherings - complete with additional fixed seating while leaving ample room for pets/kids to play - or put in a pool if you wish!
With astute attention to detail, this stunning home has been lovingly created with a warm neutral palate, offering additional notable features such as solar panels, ducted heating, and evaporative cooling, this home is ready for you to walk in - unpack and simply enjoy!
Acacia Ridge is an extremely popular family friendly estate with Botanic Ridge Primary School already receiving rave reviews and the planned shopping hub will without a doubt enhance the estate upon it's completion. Description:
Large Family Home on 2.95 Acres
Situated in the quiet country township of Cardinia within a stones throw to the cricket oval, tennis courts, general store and Primary School the commanding residence is set well back from the road in a perfect elevated position on the magnificent almost 3 acre estate. This convenient location is also only a short drive to the hustle and bustle of the surrounding suburbs of Pakenham, Officer, Beaconsfield, Clyde, Koo Wee Rup, Cranbourne and Tooradin. Offering a substantial residence with numerous living zones this home is perfect for the large family and those wanting space for animals, motorbikes and vehicles. The family friendly layout ensures that everyone has space and offers;
* Numerous living zones include a tiled family room featuring barn doors and central meals area adjoining the kitchen.
* Massive lounge and rumpus room complete with a wood fire ideal for the upcoming cold winter nights.
* The impressive kitchen is the central meeting point has everything needed to cook up a storm including an island bench, loads of cupboard space, 900mm cooktop, 900mm oven, glass splashback and a dishwasher to help clean up.
* Four bedrooms plus a study, ideal as a nursery or fifth bedroom.
* The master bedroom has a walk in robe and a hotel quality ensuite complete with a huge bathtub and a double basin.
* The remaining bedrooms are a great size and have enough room for everything the kids need.
* The family bathroom has a separate toilet ideal for guests.
* Ducted reverse cycle heating and cooling throughout.
* Quality fixtures and fittings.
Outside is where all the fun is to be had;
* Massive pitched roof entertaining area complete with in built BBQ, wood heater, lighting and ceiling fans provides the ideal space to entertain family and friends whilst watching the kids play in the backyard.
* Heaps of lawn space with an above ground pool.
* Car accommodation includes a double carport plus a large 7.5m x 12m steel shed, perfect for those needing to accommodate extra vehicles, boats, trailers, caravans, or just extra storage.
* Secure area for your four-legged friends.
* Veggie garden and chook pen. Eat your own produce!
* Large paddock ideal for animals or motorbikes plus a holding yard.
This home has so much to offer for the large family! Properties like this are extremely hard to find so be sure to book an inspection. Check out the video tour!

Walk to the Shops, Train Station & Schools from this Renovated Beauty!
Nested in a peaceful court with an abundance of services nearby including schools, shops and public transport all within walking distance, this property will be a fantastic home or investment property. Situated on a spacious 530sqm (approx.) allotment, you will love the fully renovated kitchen, fresh paint and recently installed carpet for years to come.
This property is brimming with features, including:
• Three bedrooms, all with built in robes and ceiling fans
• Master bedroom includes ensuite, spacious walk in robe and alfresco access
• Three spacious living areas including large living room, formal dining/family area and open plan meals and family area
• Fully renovated modern kitchen featuring soft close drawers, new stainless steel appliances including 900mm oven and stovetop, dishwasher and plenty of cupboard space
• Ducted heating throughout, reverse cycle air conditioning unit, electric fire place and multiple ceiling fans will keep you comfortable all year round
• Main bathroom features a bathtub and separate toilet
• Separate laundry with plenty of built in storage and external access
• Spacious alfresco flows from the kitchen and meals area and the Master bedroom and is perfect for all year round entertaining
• Landscaped backyard includes lawn and a shed to store your outdoor belongings
• Oversized remote controlled double car garage
Completing the picture is the brilliant location of this home as you are within walking distance or a short drive away to all the essential amenities. For parents, Courtenay Gardens Primary School & Bluebird Early Education are just around the corner whilst Lyndhurst Secondary is around a 20 minute walk. Shop till you drop with Thompson Parkway Shopping Centre only a 5 minute walk away, Cranbourne Home Shopping Centre a 8 minute walk whilst Springhill Shopping Centre is a 20 minute walk away. Access to the South Gippsland Hwy is only a short 2 minute drive away with Merinda Park Train Station is a 23 minute walk or a 4 minute drive.

Description:
Neat & Complete Perfectly Positioned!
This spotlessly presented 2 years old home represents an outstanding opportunity to purchase your first home, investment property or somewhere to downsize to. With a spacious open floorplan design, this immaculately presented home is sure to impress from the moment you walk through the front door. With n abundance of natural light yet offering privacy both inside and out, some of the stylish modern features include:
- 3 good size bedrooms Master complete with en-suite & WIR with all remaining bedrooms having BIR's and serviced by the second bathroom.
- A fully appointed kitchen featuring stone benchtop, quality stainless steel appliances and ample bench space and storage.
- Low maintenance back yard featuring concrete outdoor entertaining area.
- A garage with remote roller door and internal access.
-Ducted heating plus split system air-conditioning.
Ideally located in one this area's newest and most sought-after estates, "Ambrosia", you have quick easy access to the Monash Freeway, Eastlink and Mornington Peninsula and central Cranbourne is only a few minutes away. Everything you need is right at your doorstep and an inspection will not disappoint but be quick as this is priced to sell.

Description:
COURT LOCATION CLOSE TO EVERYTHING!
CRANBOURNE WEST - Sitting at the base of a quiet court location, this home would be perfect for a first home buyer, investor or perhaps someone looking to downsize. Surrounded by well presented homes and walking distance to public transport, Cranbourne West primary school, Shandhurst shopping village and parklands.
Upon entry, you are immediately taken with the amount of natural light and open plan living. Offset by the floating floorboards, the living area exudes homeliness and comfort making it a space you will love to spend time relaxing or enjoying with family and friends.
The spacious open plan kitchen and dining area offers an ideal setting for meals. The kitchen itself offers a dishwasher, gas stovetop and plenty of bench space which doubles as a breakfast bar. The kitchen is equipped with everything you need to whip up a delicious family meal.
The second living area is well sized and looks out onto the enormous pergola area. Perfect for entertaining and with easily maintained gardens, the backyard space will fit friends, family, pets and still have room for little ones to run around! The garden shed is an added bonus and a great space for extra storage.
Features include:
- Ducted heating
- Split system
- Single lock-up garage with rear access
- 622m2 allotment
Cranbourne West is a fast developing and family-friendly area. Offering a great combination of schools including Cranbourne West Primary, and St Peter's College. The area provides easy access to main arterial roads including the Monash Freeway and East Link and is very popular with families and investors. Access to public transport including Merinda Park Station and Cranbourne Train Station is close by.
